sql:
SELECT report_id 
FROM reports 
ORDER BY report_id;

external_knowledge:
- The statistics provided for each team (total assigned reports, resolved reports, and open reports) are only for teams that have at least one report assigned to them; 
- Resolved reports are those with a status of 1 (closed) in the reports table; 
- Open reports are those with a status of 0 (open) in the reports table.
